Tally licensing
===============

Tally contains two kinds of material, licensed separately.

1. The company directory
------------------------
Everything under `Companies/` is public reference information about companies,
drawn from public sources.

Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).
You may copy, redistribute, adapt and build on it, including commercially,
provided you give appropriate credit to MilUX (https://milux.co.uk).

Full text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode


2. MilUX-authored materials
---------------------------
The company page template (`Company Page Template.md`), the tag taxonomy
(`Tagging.md`), the guide (`Tally Guide.md`), and the Tally search viewer
(when added) are original works by MilUX.

Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International
(CC BY-NC 4.0). You may use, share and adapt them for non-commercial purposes
with attribution to MilUX. Commercial use requires prior written permission
from MilUX (contact@milux.co.uk).

Full text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/legalcode


